abstract: Nahant consists of two peninsular islands, called Great Nahant and Little Nahant. abstract: AFFRAY AND DEATH.--On Saturday, the 19th Inst., FRANCIS J. KING killed JOHN DOUGHERTY, in Brandenburg, Ky.
